  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join our Discord!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hoofobia is a chaotic 1v3 multiplayer game of deception and survival. Enrage the hunter in multiple game modes with a dozen maps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Imposter Hunt:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Ram the hunter or wait for him to shoot too many AI deer and he will go insane.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467300/extras/94f37fa2eaa39544556ad3d0ae543fcc.poster.avif?t=1753507983\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467300/extras/94f37fa2eaa39544556ad3d0ae543fcc.webm?t=1753507983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467300/extras/94f37fa2eaa39544556ad3d0ae543fcc.mp4?t=1753507983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stay Close:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Attack the hunter and stay within his proximity to slowly earn points.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467300/extras/57518433d74a3e2a5ee232ba36ea901e.poster.avif?t=1753507983\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467300/extras/57518433d74a3e2a5ee232ba36ea901e.webm?t=1753507983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467300/extras/57518433d74a3e2a5ee232ba36ea901e.mp4?t=1753507983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hit & Run:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Ram the hunter, stay inside his bubble for 20 seconds and then escape to earn a point.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467300/extras/6a686952e5ca2817133a6eaf1e5d7b99.poster.avif?t=1753507983\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467300/extras/6a686952e5ca2817133a6eaf1e5d7b99.webm?t=1753507983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467300/extras/6a686952e5ca2817133a6eaf1e5d7b99.mp4?t=1753507983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hoofobia is a chaotic 1v3 multiplayer game of deception and survival. Enrage the hunter in multiple game modes with a dozen maps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Imposter Hunt:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Ram the hunter or wait for him to shoot too many AI deer and he will go insane.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467300/extras/94f37fa2eaa39544556ad3d0ae543fcc.poster.avif?t=1753507983\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467300/extras/94f37fa2eaa39544556ad3d0ae543fcc.webm?t=1753507983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467300/extras/94f37fa2eaa39544556ad3d0ae543fcc.mp4?t=1753507983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stay Close:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Attack the hunter and stay within his proximity to slowly earn points.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467300/extras/57518433d74a3e2a5ee232ba36ea901e.poster.avif?t=1753507983\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467300/extras/57518433d74a3e2a5ee232ba36ea901e.webm?t=1753507983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467300/extras/57518433d74a3e2a5ee232ba36ea901e.mp4?t=1753507983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hit & Run:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Ram the hunter, stay inside his bubble for 20 seconds and then escape to earn a point.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467300/extras/6a686952e5ca2817133a6eaf1e5d7b99.poster.avif?t=1753507983\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467300/extras/6a686952e5ca2817133a6eaf1e5d7b99.webm?t=1753507983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467300/extras/6a686952e5ca2817133a6eaf1e5d7b99.mp4?t=1753507983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
